## Add Three Revenue-Multiplying Features

### Feature 1: Scrap Price Data Platform (The "Bloomberg of Scrap")

| What | Detail |
|---|---|
| What you build | Real-time scrap price tracking across 20+ Indian cities for 15+ material types |
| Data source | Your own customers (they enter buy/sell prices daily) + web scraping + MCX data |
| Revenue model | Free basic prices (brings traffic) + Premium analytics ₹999/month |
| Why it's powerful | You own the DATA. Every trader checking prices sees YOUR platform. This becomes your marketplace on-ramp. |
| Competition | Nobody does this. Traders call 10 people every morning. You replace 10 phone calls with one dashboard. |

### Feature 2: EPR Compliance Module

| What | Detail |
|---|---|
| What you build | Auto-generate CPCB/SPCB quarterly reports, EPR certificates with QR codes, compliance tracking |
| Who pays | Recyclers (₹2,000-5,000/month extra) AND brands/PROs (₹20,000-1,00,000/month) |
| Why it's powerful | Regulation FORCES adoption. As EPR enforcement tightens, every recycler MUST have digital compliance. First-mover wins. |
| Moat | Once a recycler's 2 years of compliance data is in your system, switching cost is enormous. |

### Feature 3: Marketplace (Buy/Sell Scrap Digitally)

| What | Detail |
|---|---|
| What you build | Buyers post requirements ("need 5 tons copper scrap, Chennai"). Sellers list available material. Platform matches and facilitates. |
| Revenue model | 1-2% transaction fee on deals closed through platform |
| Why it's powerful | Network effects — more buyers attract more sellers attract more buyers. Winner takes most. |
| How it connects to your existing product | Your recycler customers already log their output material. One click to "list for sale" on your marketplace. Zero extra effort for them. |

